name: Orange 3 in 1 Stretchy Bracelet
description: Very similar to the orange 4 in 1 Stretchy Bracelet, only much less dense, so even lighter. It has an interesting property that if you put it on and then flip it over, there's a slightly different pattern on the other side. It's like having two designs in one! Made of 16 guage orange anodized aluminum and orange edpm rings, and even stretchier than the 4 in 1 bracelet. Comes in small, medium, or large. (message me if you need help choosing a size)
